<p>We collect only the information that is essential for establishing and maintaining connections to our backend
    services. This may include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>IP address</li>
    <li>Connection timestamps</li>
    <li>General location data for telemetry purposes</li>
    <li>Account information (e.g., email address, account ID) used solely for rate limiting and features that require
        user identification</li>
</ul>

<h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
<p>We do not collect the following information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Payment information (e.g., credit card details)</li>
    <li>Browsing history</li>
    <li>Any other data not necessary for establishing connections to our backend services</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>The information we collect is used exclusively for the purpose of establishing and maintaining connections to our
    backend services. We do not share, sell, or distribute your personal data to third parties.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about anything, please contact us at infinitepixelboard@gmail.com</p>